Issue body actions

### Description

Hi guys. 
I am stuck. 
Wails cli build don't see a packages build's tags for other platforms like "+windows" 
But go build works fine. Could you advice me how to solve it? 
I am newbie in desktop apps, so maybe I do something wrong?

### To Reproduce

* Init wails project
* Add module: go get github.com/akrylysov/pogreb@v0.10.1
* Run: GOOS=windows GOARCH=amd64 wails build -clean -platform windows
* Got error: ../../../../../pkg/mod/github.com/akrylysov/pogreb@v0.10.1/fs/os\_mmap\_windows.go:23:13: undeclared name maxMmapSize for array length

### Expected behaviour

Its not an error

### Screenshots

_No response_

### Attempted Fixes

I tried different tags for wails build but no success.

But clean go build works fine 
GOOS=windows GOARCH=amd64 go build -tags desktop,production -ldflags "-w -s -H windowsgui" -o example.exe

